Class RemoteProjectSettingsUpdateRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.ria.web.ajax.dto.remote.RemoteProjectSettingsUpdateRequest
  • public class RemoteProjectSettingsUpdateRequest
extends Object
    Used to handle requests from the UI to update settings for a remote sync'd project. The field is the attribute to be update, and the value is the value to set to that field.
